Universal Hamilton method that hosts a server receiving JSON
string packets from the HamiltonInterface class. The method
continuously loops over conditional statements, first checking
which command was sent e.g. "ChannelTipPickUp", then extracting
parameters from the JSON string. After the command is performed,
a response string is returned to the interface.
